<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />剛才天上出現了好多流星喔<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
不知道等一下會不會又有，<delay8 />
讓我都捨不得移開視線了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我剛才因為想看流星，<delay8 />
就一直抬頭看著天空<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以脖子就<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為流星實在太美了，<delay20 />
我看得太入神，<delay8 />
都忘了要許願呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看見彩虹會讓人有種幸福的感覺，<delay20 />
那如果和身邊的人一起看同一道彩虹，<delay8 />
幸福是不是也會加倍呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">好漂亮的彩虹喔<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺看著它，心裡那些小小的煩惱<delay8 />
也都跟著煙消雲散了<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雨過天晴後掛在天邊的彩虹，<delay20 />
簡直就像是<delay8 />太陽的祝福呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />竟然能夠同時看到兩道彩虹，<delay8 />
今天真是太幸運了～<delay20 />
我總覺得<delay8 />今天還會遇到很多好事呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />同時出現兩道彩虹，<delay8 />這真是太美了<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是<delay8 />看到不常見的現象出現，<delay20 />
就會<delay8 /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />讓人不禁覺得<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這可能是什麼徵兆呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">天空同時出現兩道彩虹，<delay20 />
而這罕見的奇景正緩緩地消失<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓人忍不住想看到最後一刻呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="004_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">冬季夜空中絢爛的極光<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這大自然所展現的神祕瞬間，<delay20 />
讓人完全無法移開視線呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />夜空就像戴上了極光織成的面紗一樣<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那薄紗之下<anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />是不是藏著什麼<delay8 />
不想讓我們看見的秘密呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />冬季漆黑寒冷的天空，<delay20 />
反而將華麗又絢爛的極光<delay8 />
襯托得更加美麗呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="005_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那艘在空中留下一道雲彩的飛機，<delay20 />
究竟飛去了哪座島呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">在藍天中筆直延伸的飛機雲<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總覺得給人一種<delay8 />
清爽的感覺呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看著天上的飛機雲，<delay20 />
讓我突然很想去旅行呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="006_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好美的一輪明月<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
感覺滿月的美<delay8 />
也豐富了我的心靈呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">滿月明亮柔和的光芒和太陽的強光相比，<delay20 />
有種太陽所沒有的魅力呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且還可以慢慢欣賞喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在滿月高掛的夜空下散步，<delay8 />
感覺月光讓整個世界都更浪漫了呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這可是我<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />每個月一次的樂趣喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>